Would you mind adding the definition of Jacobson space in the topology folder, following https://stacks.math.columbia.edu/tag/005T
Done, I travelled to the past and opened #18243
Awesome. In that case, could you please make this PR depend on that one?

I think the two PRs can be reviewed and merged separately though. As this does not immediately imply that `Spec R` is Jacobson (despite the misleading comment, I will remove it) and the equivalence `IsJacobson R <-> JacobsonSpace (Spec R)` will still need to come in a later PR.
